    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-0.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Jin is sixteen and starts working at her father's restaurant.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.197,
        "duration": 4.197,
        "sentenceIndex": 0
      },
      {
        "text": "Her father opened the business at twenty-one with help from his parents.",
        "startTime": 4.197,
        "endTime": 9.15,
        "duration": 4.953,
        "sentenceIndex": 1
      },
      {
        "text": "He left Greece as a teenager and worked in restaurants.",
        "startTime": 9.15,
        "endTime": 12.934,
        "duration": 3.784,
        "sentenceIndex": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "Now he has his own place.",
        "startTime": 12.934,
        "endTime": 14.654,
        "duration": 1.72,
        "sentenceIndex": 3
      },
      {
        "text": "He was proud of it and smiled.",
        "startTime": 14.654,
        "endTime": 16.718,
        "duration": 2.064,
        "sentenceIndex": 4
      },
      {
        "text": "He thinks Jin will take over one day.",
        "startTime": 16.718,
        "endTime": 19.263,
        "duration": 2.545,
        "sentenceIndex": 5
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 19.263061,
    "measuredDuration": 19.263061
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b1",
    "bundleIndex": 1,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-1.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-1.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Jin has no interest in running a restaurant.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.95,
        "duration": 2.95,
        "sentenceIndex": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "She wanted to do something that felt important and good.",
        "startTime": 2.95,
        "endTime": 6.706,
        "duration": 3.755,
        "sentenceIndex": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "Something that made me feel good and gave me purpose.",
        "startTime": 6.706,
        "endTime": 10.259,
        "duration": 3.554,
        "sentenceIndex": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "When she worked at the restaurant, she sometimes cried in the bathroom.",
        "startTime": 10.259,
        "endTime": 15.17,
        "duration": 4.911,
        "sentenceIndex": 9
      },
      {
        "text": "She felt trapped and wanted to be free.",
        "startTime": 15.17,
        "endTime": 17.786,
        "duration": 2.615,
        "sentenceIndex": 10
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin feels overwhelmed and needs help to feel better.",
        "startTime": 17.786,
        "endTime": 21.272,
        "duration": 3.487,
        "sentenceIndex": 11
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 21.272404,
    "measuredDuration": 21.272404
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b2",
    "bundleIndex": 2,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-2.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-2.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She does not want to run a restaurant for her life.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.555,
        "duration": 3.555,
        "sentenceIndex": 12
      },
      {
        "text": "During summer breaks, Jin tried to find jobs in high school.",
        "startTime": 3.555,
        "endTime": 7.888,
        "duration": 4.333,
        "sentenceIndex": 13
      },
      {
        "text": "She does not want to run the register or wait tables.",
        "startTime": 7.888,
        "endTime": 11.583,
        "duration": 3.695,
        "sentenceIndex": 14
      },
      {
        "text": "Her father saw that Jin wanted to live her own life.",
        "startTime": 11.583,
        "endTime": 15.208,
        "duration": 3.625,
        "sentenceIndex": 15
      },
      {
        "text": "He understood it was important for her to follow her dreams.",
        "startTime": 15.208,
        "endTime": 19.391,
        "duration": 4.183,
        "sentenceIndex": 16
      },
      {
        "text": "He sees himself in her eyes.",
        "startTime": 19.391,
        "endTime": 21.343,
        "duration": 1.952,
        "sentenceIndex": 17
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 21.343107,
    "measuredDuration": 21.343107
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b3",
    "bundleIndex": 3,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-3.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-3.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Jin's mother has different hopes and dreams for him.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.534,
        "duration": 3.534,
        "sentenceIndex": 18
      },
      {
        "text": "She had very high standards for herself and others.",
        "startTime": 3.534,
        "endTime": 7,
        "duration": 3.466,
        "sentenceIndex": 19
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin feels pressure to make her mother proud.",
        "startTime": 7,
        "endTime": 9.991,
        "duration": 2.99,
        "sentenceIndex": 20
      },
      {
        "text": "This meant joining many activities and keeping good grades in school.",
        "startTime": 9.991,
        "endTime": 14.681,
        "duration": 4.69,
        "sentenceIndex": 21
      },
      {
        "text": "When Jin graduated third, her mother felt sad and wanted more.",
        "startTime": 14.681,
        "endTime": 19.044,
        "duration": 4.364,
        "sentenceIndex": 22
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin feels she is not enough, even with success.",
        "startTime": 19.044,
        "endTime": 22.389,
        "duration": 3.344,
        "sentenceIndex": 23
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 22.388866,
    "measuredDuration": 22.388866
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b4",
    "bundleIndex": 4,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-4.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-4.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Jin was always a very creative child.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.518,
        "duration": 2.518,
        "sentenceIndex": 24
      },
      {
        "text": "She loved reading, writing, and making art.",
        "startTime": 2.518,
        "endTime": 5.744,
        "duration": 3.226,
        "sentenceIndex": 25
      },
      {
        "text": "She tried to make art work that her mother liked.",
        "startTime": 5.744,
        "endTime": 9.078,
        "duration": 3.334,
        "sentenceIndex": 26
      },
      {
        "text": "Architecture is a good choice and seems nice.",
        "startTime": 9.078,
        "endTime": 12.14,
        "duration": 3.062,
        "sentenceIndex": 27
      },
      {
        "text": "It was creative and also good for money.",
        "startTime": 12.14,
        "endTime": 14.862,
        "duration": 2.722,
        "sentenceIndex": 28
      },
      {
        "text": "Her mother supports her interest in architecture and design.",
        "startTime": 14.862,
        "endTime": 18.945,
        "duration": 4.083,
        "sentenceIndex": 29
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 18.944694,
    "measuredDuration": 18.944694
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b5",
    "bundleIndex": 5,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-5.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-5.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "After a close friend died, Jin thought about being a therapist.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.706,
        "duration": 4.706,
        "sentenceIndex": 30
      },
      {
        "text": "She wanted to help people and make them happy.",
        "startTime": 4.706,
        "endTime": 8.032,
        "duration": 3.326,
        "sentenceIndex": 31
      },
      {
        "text": "We grow strong human connections with care and understanding.",
        "startTime": 8.032,
        "endTime": 12.444,
        "duration": 4.411,
        "sentenceIndex": 32
      },
      {
        "text": "When she talked about social sciences, her mother felt it was bad.",
        "startTime": 12.444,
        "endTime": 17.366,
        "duration": 4.923,
        "sentenceIndex": 33
      },
      {
        "text": "She asked why Jin gives up safety and comfort.",
        "startTime": 17.366,
        "endTime": 20.693,
        "duration": 3.326,
        "sentenceIndex": 34
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin feels she must make her mother happy after saying no to her father.",
        "startTime": 20.693,
        "endTime": 25.827,
        "duration": 5.134,
        "sentenceIndex": 35
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 25.827143,
    "measuredDuration": 25.827143
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b6",
    "bundleIndex": 6,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-6.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-6.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She applied to a top school and got accepted.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.294,
        "duration": 3.294,
        "sentenceIndex": 36
      },
      {
        "text": "She thinks about helping people and wants a good job.",
        "startTime": 3.294,
        "endTime": 7.173,
        "duration": 3.879,
        "sentenceIndex": 37
      },
      {
        "text": "A few days before school, Jin changed her study to sociology and psychology.",
        "startTime": 7.173,
        "endTime": 12.885,
        "duration": 5.713,
        "sentenceIndex": 38
      },
      {
        "text": "She did not tell her parents right away.",
        "startTime": 12.885,
        "endTime": 15.813,
        "duration": 2.928,
        "sentenceIndex": 39
      },
      {
        "text": "She was afraid they would be disappointed.",
        "startTime": 15.813,
        "endTime": 18.887,
        "duration": 3.074,
        "sentenceIndex": 40
      },
      {
        "text": "She knew they wanted her to pick a safe way to succeed.",
        "startTime": 18.887,
        "endTime": 22.913,
        "duration": 4.026,
        "sentenceIndex": 41
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 22.91254,
    "measuredDuration": 22.91254
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b7",
    "bundleIndex": 7,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-7.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-7.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "They pushed her hard and wanted her to do well.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.364,
        "duration": 3.364,
        "sentenceIndex": 42
      },
      {
        "text": "They wanted the best for her, but they hurt her spirit.",
        "startTime": 3.364,
        "endTime": 7.45,
        "duration": 4.086,
        "sentenceIndex": 43
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin and other children want to make their parents proud.",
        "startTime": 7.45,
        "endTime": 11.457,
        "duration": 4.008,
        "sentenceIndex": 44
      },
      {
        "text": "They wanted their parents to feel their sacrifice was worth it.",
        "startTime": 11.457,
        "endTime": 15.966,
        "duration": 4.509,
        "sentenceIndex": 45
      },
      {
        "text": "But what does that really mean.",
        "startTime": 15.966,
        "endTime": 18.184,
        "duration": 2.219,
        "sentenceIndex": 46
      },
      {
        "text": "Did they follow their parents' path or make their own.",
        "startTime": 18.184,
        "endTime": 22.049,
        "duration": 3.865,
        "sentenceIndex": 47
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 22.048866,
    "measuredDuration": 22.048866
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b8",
    "bundleIndex": 8,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-8.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-8.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "The problem is often harder because of cultural differences.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.11,
        "duration": 4.11,
        "sentenceIndex": 48
      },
      {
        "text": "Many immigrant parents come from places with group cultures.",
        "startTime": 4.11,
        "endTime": 8.22,
        "duration": 4.11,
        "sentenceIndex": 49
      },
      {
        "text": "These societies focus on community and help each other.",
        "startTime": 8.22,
        "endTime": 11.987,
        "duration": 3.767,
        "sentenceIndex": 50
      },
      {
        "text": "Inheriting a family business is what people expect.",
        "startTime": 11.987,
        "endTime": 15.481,
        "duration": 3.493,
        "sentenceIndex": 51
      },
      {
        "text": "People do not encourage individual dreams.",
        "startTime": 15.481,
        "endTime": 18.358,
        "duration": 2.877,
        "sentenceIndex": 52
      },
      {
        "text": "Their children are in the United States and they have freedom.",
        "startTime": 18.358,
        "endTime": 22.604,
        "duration": 4.247,
        "sentenceIndex": 53
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 22.60449,
    "measuredDuration": 22.60449
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b9",
    "bundleIndex": 9,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-9.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-9.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "They want to be themselves but feel pressure to fit in.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.916,
        "duration": 3.916,
        "sentenceIndex": 54
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin chose her own path and did not take her father's business.",
        "startTime": 3.916,
        "endTime": 8.33,
        "duration": 4.414,
        "sentenceIndex": 55
      },
      {
        "text": "She often worried her parents did not feel appreciated.",
        "startTime": 8.33,
        "endTime": 12.245,
        "duration": 3.916,
        "sentenceIndex": 56
      },
      {
        "text": "But this is not true at all.",
        "startTime": 12.245,
        "endTime": 14.239,
        "duration": 1.993,
        "sentenceIndex": 57
      },
      {
        "text": "Choosing her dreams shows her gratitude and happiness.",
        "startTime": 14.239,
        "endTime": 18.083,
        "duration": 3.844,
        "sentenceIndex": 58
      },
      {
        "text": "She has a choice because they made sacrifices for her.",
        "startTime": 18.083,
        "endTime": 21.928,
        "duration": 3.844,
        "sentenceIndex": 59
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 21.927823,
    "measuredDuration": 21.927823
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b10",
    "bundleIndex": 10,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-10.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-10.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "They made it possible for her to define her future.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.499,
        "duration": 3.499,
        "sentenceIndex": 60
      },
      {
        "text": "Was she really meant to follow them when they wanted her choices.",
        "startTime": 3.499,
        "endTime": 7.959,
        "duration": 4.46,
        "sentenceIndex": 61
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin's parents came to the United States with very little.",
        "startTime": 7.959,
        "endTime": 11.87,
        "duration": 3.911,
        "sentenceIndex": 62
      },
      {
        "text": "Her father left Greece when he was a teenager.",
        "startTime": 11.87,
        "endTime": 15.027,
        "duration": 3.156,
        "sentenceIndex": 63
      },
      {
        "text": "Her mother grew up poor and worked on farms with her parents.",
        "startTime": 15.027,
        "endTime": 19.212,
        "duration": 4.186,
        "sentenceIndex": 64
      },
      {
        "text": "They worked many hours each day for the life they wanted.",
        "startTime": 19.212,
        "endTime": 23.123,
        "duration": 3.911,
        "sentenceIndex": 65
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 23.123424,
    "measuredDuration": 23.123424
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b11",
    "bundleIndex": 11,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-11.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-11.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "They wanted Jin to have chances they did not have.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.492,
        "duration": 3.492,
        "sentenceIndex": 66
      },
      {
        "text": "They wanted her to choose safe paths and be happy.",
        "startTime": 3.492,
        "endTime": 6.985,
        "duration": 3.492,
        "sentenceIndex": 67
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin is a doctor and helps many sick people.",
        "startTime": 6.985,
        "endTime": 9.988,
        "duration": 3.003,
        "sentenceIndex": 68
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin is a lawyer and helps people with their problems.",
        "startTime": 9.988,
        "endTime": 13.69,
        "duration": 3.702,
        "sentenceIndex": 69
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin is an engineer and works on important projects.",
        "startTime": 13.69,
        "endTime": 17.252,
        "duration": 3.562,
        "sentenceIndex": 70
      },
      {
        "text": "They understood these jobs and liked them.",
        "startTime": 17.252,
        "endTime": 20.186,
        "duration": 2.934,
        "sentenceIndex": 71
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 20.186122,
    "measuredDuration": 20.186122
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b12",
    "bundleIndex": 12,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-12.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-12.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "These jobs promised success and made people happy.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.78,
        "duration": 3.78,
        "sentenceIndex": 72
      },
      {
        "text": "Jin does not know what people do in an office.",
        "startTime": 3.78,
        "endTime": 7.257,
        "duration": 3.477,
        "sentenceIndex": 73
      },
      {
        "text": "She never sees creative jobs and does not know them.",
        "startTime": 7.257,
        "endTime": 11.188,
        "duration": 3.931,
        "sentenceIndex": 74
      },
      {
        "text": "She only knew about jobs with clear paths and plans.",
        "startTime": 11.188,
        "endTime": 15.119,
        "duration": 3.931,
        "sentenceIndex": 75
      },
      {
        "text": "Law is important and helps people live together.",
        "startTime": 15.119,
        "endTime": 18.748,
        "duration": 3.629,
        "sentenceIndex": 76
      },
      {
        "text": "Medicine helps people feel better and stay healthy.",
        "startTime": 18.748,
        "endTime": 22.603,
        "duration": 3.855,
        "sentenceIndex": 77
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 22.603084,
    "measuredDuration": 22.603084
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b13",
    "bundleIndex": 13,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-13.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-13.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Engineering is the design and building of machines and structures.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.442,
        "duration": 4.442,
        "sentenceIndex": 78
      },
      {
        "text": "Architecture is the art of designing buildings and spaces.",
        "startTime": 4.442,
        "endTime": 8.345,
        "duration": 3.903,
        "sentenceIndex": 79
      },
      {
        "text": "Her parents and their friends understood these jobs well.",
        "startTime": 8.345,
        "endTime": 12.181,
        "duration": 3.836,
        "sentenceIndex": 80
      },
      {
        "text": "These jobs looked safe and good for people.",
        "startTime": 12.181,
        "endTime": 15.075,
        "duration": 2.894,
        "sentenceIndex": 81
      },
      {
        "text": "When Jin started college, she met other students like her.",
        "startTime": 15.075,
        "endTime": 19.129,
        "duration": 4.053,
        "sentenceIndex": 82
      },
      {
        "text": "They talked about their families and shared their stories.",
        "startTime": 19.129,
        "endTime": 23.032,
        "duration": 3.903,
        "sentenceIndex": 83
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 23.032313,
    "measuredDuration": 23.032313
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b14",
    "bundleIndex": 14,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-14.mp3",
    "audioPath": "cultural-bridge-2/A1/bundle-14.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "People feel pressure to succeed in America and other places.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.921,
        "duration": 3.921,
        "sentenceIndex": 84
      },
      {
        "text": "They feel guilty about having things their parents did not have.",
        "startTime": 3.921,
        "endTime": 8.103,
        "duration": 4.182,
        "sentenceIndex": 85
      },
      {
        "text": "Students feel pressure to do well because of their parents' sacrifices.",
        "startTime": 8.103,
        "endTime": 12.743,
        "duration": 4.64,
        "sentenceIndex": 86
      },
      {
        "text": "It can feel hard to breathe sometimes.",
        "startTime": 12.743,
        "endTime": 15.226,
        "duration": 2.483,
        "sentenceIndex": 87
      },
      {
        "text": "A friend told Jin her mother said it is not too late.",
        "startTime": 15.226,
        "endTime": 18.69,
        "duration": 3.463,
        "sentenceIndex": 88
      },
      {
        "text": "No matter what Jin did, it was never enough.",
        "startTime": 18.69,
        "endTime": 21.715,
        "duration": 3.025,
        "sentenceIndex": 89
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 21.714853,
    "measuredDuration": 21.714853
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b15",
    "bundleIndex": 15,
